**CSS для `.mm-related` и `.mm-related-link`** (добавлять в `<style>` каждой iPhone-страницы):

```css
.mm-block .mm-related {
  display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; margin-top: 14px;
}
.mm-block .mm-related-link {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  padding: 10px 18px; border-radius: 999px;
  background: #F3F3F3; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
  color: #2C2C2C; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500;
  text-decoration: none; white-space: nowrap;
  transition: background 0.18s, border-color 0.18s;
}
.mm-block .mm-related-link:hover {
  background: #EAEAEA; border-color: #d0d0d0; color: #000;
}
@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .mm-block .mm-related { gap: 8px; }
  .mm-block .mm-related-link { font-size: 13px; padding: 9px 14px; }
}
```

